I can only hope

20
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,240
my mom's too busy with work

21
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:29,159
to check the chat messages.

22
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,960
As long as she doesn't push it,

23
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:32,839
my dad won't force me

24
00:02:32,839 --> 00:02:33,719
to sign up.

25
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:34,800
My dad is

26
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:35,879
a bit different from other parents.

27
00:02:36,319 --> 00:02:37,559
He says studying is like

28
00:02:37,559 --> 00:02:39,080
competing with oneself.

29
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:39,759
So no need to stress

30
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:40,839
over short-term wins and losses.

31
00:02:40,920 --> 00:02:41,839
Stop showing off.

32
00:02:45,279 --> 00:02:46,159
I'm not going.

33
00:02:46,159 --> 00:02:47,439
I'm joining the performance.

34
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,520
Your mom was called to school.

35
00:02:54,599 --> 00:02:55,879
With your grades right now,

36
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:57,240
you have to push yourself

37
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:58,319
and put in

38
00:02:58,520 --> 00:02:59,360
some extra effort.

39
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:01,520
Didn't you say studying is like a marathon?

40
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,080
Don't sweat

41
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,279
the small stuff.

42
00:03:04,719 --> 00:03:07,400
I meant that strategically.

43
00:03:07,599 --> 00:03:08,520
I mean,

44
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,920
one should have

45
00:03:09,920 --> 00:03:10,800
a long-term goal.

46
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,719
And right now, your goal

47
00:03:11,719 --> 00:03:12,719
is the high-school entrance exam,

48
00:03:12,719 --> 00:03:13,279
right?

49
